    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time to be a hero! Your homeland has been invaded by a megalomaniac conqueror. As the wielder of a mechanical marvel, The Mighty Claw, it’s your job to master its powers and beat back the forces of the tyrant!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Mighty Claw is a 2D platformer that takes grappling hook mechanics to a new level. Attach your claw to any surface and use tons of cool grapple moves to jump, swing, and zip your way through masterfully designed challenges across a colorful cartoon world full of a wacky cast of characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386380/extras/65e3cbc9426cbef689710a2f3d0cf1b9.poster.avif?t=1770239692\" width=800 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386380/extras/65e3cbc9426cbef689710a2f3d0cf1b9.webm?t=1770239692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386380/extras/65e3cbc9426cbef689710a2f3d0cf1b9.mp4?t=1770239692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the Claw and pull off cool moves. Swing like crazy through mechanically diverse levels! Grab enemies and throw them into other enemies! Precision movement, momentum control, and quick thinking are rewarded.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386380/extras/e26f6470b06f4a83948ad3464f1383d0.poster.avif?t=1770239692\" width=800 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386380/extras/e26f6470b06f4a83948ad3464f1383d0.webm?t=1770239692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386380/extras/e26f6470b06f4a83948ad3464f1383d0.mp4?t=1770239692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find your unique playstyle and solve challenges your way! Spin, jump, zip, and climb - chain fluid movement and find creative solutions! Free-form gameplay encourages experimentation and skill expression.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386380/extras/3f276b8430f31655e79836f394178231.poster.avif?t=1770239692\" width=800 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386380/extras/3f276b8430f31655e79836f394178231.webm?t=1770239692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386380/extras/3f276b8430f31655e79836f394178231.mp4?t=1770239692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tons of cool grapple moves to perform</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple creative solutions for the challenges of the game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smooth swinging controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wacky cast of characters inhabiting a colorful cartoon world</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upbeat, catchy soundtrack that keeps you hooked</p></li></ul>",
